<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 myn ạlly wạ̉nạ zʿlạn byfrḥny
 myn ạlly wạ̉nạ wạ̉nạ tʿbạn byryḥny
 myn ạlly ʿmrh ʿmrh mạ byjrḥny
 gẖyrh hw ḥbyby yswʿ
 lmạ ạ̉ṣḥạby ykrhwny wyʿmlwạ sẖlẗ wyḍrbwny
 wymsẖwạ wlwḥdy ysybwny ybqy̱ ạ̉rwḥ lmyn
 bạbạ wmạmạ msẖ fạḍyyn wạ̹kẖwạty msẖ sạỷlyn
 ṭb lmạ ḥạjẗ tḍạyqny ybqy̱ ạ̉rwḥ mlyn</lyrics>
<title>myn ạlly wạ̉nạ</title>
